snippet: Kevin Youkilis, back at Fenway Park on Monday as a member of the White Sox, was never a controversial figure for the Red Sox, not until the end, and even then, reluctantly.
abstract: Tyler Kepner On Baseball column notes that Chicago White Sox infielder Kevin Youkilis was cheered by fans at Fenway park when he returned to play the Boston Red Sox after being traded.
lead_paragraph: Kevin Youkilis, back at Fenway Park on Monday as a member of the White Sox, was never a controversial figure for the Red Sox, not until the end, and even then, reluctantly.

headline.seo: In Youkilis’s Return, Plenty of Cheers and No Regrets
headline.main: Plenty of Cheers in Return, and No Regrets on Leaving
headline.print_headline: Plenty of Cheers, And No Regrets
